org.apache.hadoop.hbase.util

Enum Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Order>
      • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.util.Order
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Order>

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
public enum Order
extends Enum<Order>
    Used to describe or modify the lexicographical sort order of a byte[]. Default ordering is considered ASCENDING. The order of a byte[] can be inverted, resulting in DESCENDING order, by replacing each byte with its 1's compliment.
